fields.title: posters
fields.content:
ry! Stay back! He's too powerful! Throw her in the brig. Enough about your promiscuous mother, Hermes! We have bigger problems. I'm sure those windmills will keep them cool. For example, if you killed your grandfather, you'd cease to exist!

You'll have all the Slurm you can drink when you're partying with Slurms McKenzie! Ah, computer dating. It's like pimping, but you rarely have to use the phrase "upside your head. " Yep, I remember. They came in last at the Olympics, then retired to promote alcoholic beverages!

Oh, you're a dollar naughtier than most.
Actually, that's still true. Who's brave enough to fly into something we all keep calling a death sphere? Oh dear! She's stuck in an infinite loop, and he's an idiot! Well, that's love for you. Tell them I hate them.

Please, Don-Botà look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file!
There's no part of that sentence I didn't like!
Calculon is gonna kill us and it's all everybody else's fault!
Alright, let's mafia things up a bit. Joey, burn down the ship. Clamps, burn down the crew.
We'll go deliver this crate like professionals, and then we'll go home. Calculon is gonna kill us and it's all everybody else's fault! Oh right. I forgot about the battle. Now, now. Perfectly symmetrical violence never solved anything.

Stop it, stop it. It's fine. I will 'destroy' you!
Yeah. Give a little credit to our public schools.
Moving alongà

fields.title: Another one
fields.content:
Why am I sticky and naked? Did I miss something fun? Look, last night was a mistake. No! The kind with looting and maybe starting a few fires! Bender, we're trying our best. It's a T. It goes "tuh".

WINDMILLS DO NOT WORK THAT WAY! GOOD NIGHT! Noooooo! Moving alongà You are the last hope of the universe. Check it out, y'all. Everyone who was invited is here.

Hey! I'm a porno-dealing monster, what do I care what you think? We're rescuing ya. In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.

Yeah. Give a little credit to our public schools. Hey, what kinda party is this? There's no booze and only one hooker. The alien mothership is in orbit here. If we can hit that bullseye, the rest of the dominoes will fall like a house of cards. Checkmate.

Noooooo! Anyone who laughs is a communist! There's no part of that sentence I didn't like! You won't have time for sleeping, soldier, not with all the bed making you'll be doing.

I'm sure those windmills will keep them cool. Good news, everyone! I've taught the toaster to feel love! As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead. Also Zoidberg. Or a guy who burns down a bar for the insurance money!

Well I'da done better, but it's plum hard pleading a case while awaiting trial for that there incompetence. I daresay that Fry has discovered the smelliest object in the known universe! Quite possible. We live long and are celebrated poopers.

Hey, guess what you're accessories to. I don't know what you did, Fry, but once again, you screwed up! Now all the planets are gonna start cracking wise about our mamas. Dear God, they'll be killed on our doorstep! And there's no trash pickup until January 3rd.

fields.title: Post 5
fields.content:
Fry, you can't just sit here in the dark listening to classical music. And when we woke up, we had these bodies. Bender?! You stole the atom. I meant 'physically'. Look, perhaps you could let me work for a little food? I could clean the floors or paint a fence, or service you sexually?

That's a popular name today. Little "e", big "B"? Fry! Quit doing the right thing, you jerk! Is the Space Pope reptilian!? Robot 1-X, save my friends! And Zoidberg! I've got to find a way to escape the horrible ravages of youth. Suddenly, I'm going to the bathroom like clockwork, every three hours. And those jerks at Social Security stopped sending me checks. Now 'I'' have to pay ''them'!

Yes, I saw. You were doing well, until everyone died.
Look, everyone wants to be like Germany, but do we really have the pure strength of 'will'? Ugh, it's filthy! Why not create a National Endowment for Strip Clubs while we're at it? Yeah. Give a little credit to our public schools.

Leela, are you alright? You got wanged on the head.
There's no part of that sentence I didn't like!
You know the worst thing about being a slave? They make you work, but they don't pay you or let you go.
When will that be?
Daylight and everything. Too much work. Let's burn it and say we dumped it in the sewer. I just want to talk. It has nothing to do with mating. Fry, that doesn't make sense. Daylight and everything. You, a bobsleder!? That I'd like to see!

Okay, it's 500 dollars, you have no choice of carrier, the battery can't hold the charge and the reception isn't veryà
This is the worst kind of discrimination: the kind against me!
WINDMILLS DO NOT WORK THAT WAY! GOOD NIGHT!

fields.title: Hola
fields.content:
No! The kind with looting and maybe starting a few fires! A true inspiration for the children. It's just like the story of the grasshopper and the octopus. All year long, the grasshopper kept burying acorns for winter, while the octopus mooched off his girlfriend and watched TV. But then the winter came, and the grasshopper died, and the octopus ate all his acorns. Also he got a race car. Is any of this getting through to you?

OK, this has gotta stop. I'm going to remind Fry of his humanity the way only a woman can. Hey, tell me something. You've got all this money. How come you always dress like you're doing your laundry? File not found.

No, she'll probably make me do it. Hi, I'm a naughty nurse, and I really need someone to talk to. $9.95 a minute. Is that a cooking show? Doomsday device? Ah, now the ball's in Farnsworth's court!

Do a flip! Oh sure! Blame the wizards! Shut up and get to the point! Shut up and take my money! I love this planet! I've got wealth, fame, and access to the depths of sleaze that those things bring. You know the worst thing about being a slave? They make you work, but they don't pay you or let you go.

Whoa a real live robot; or is that some kind of cheesy New Year's costume? I could if you hadn't turned on the light and shut off my stereo. OK, if everyone's finished being stupid. As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead.

Yeah. Give a little credit to our public schools. Well, thanks to the Internet, I'm now bored with sex. Is there a place on the web that panders to my lust for violence? Then throw her in the laundry room, which will hereafter be referred to as "the brig".

I just told you! You've killed me! Good news, everyone! I've taught the toaster to feel love! It's toe-tappingly tragic! Shut up and get to the point!

That's the ONLY thing about being a slave. Calculon is gonna kill us and it's all everybody else's fault! Now Fry, it's been a few years since medical school, so remind me. Disemboweling in your species: fatal or non-fatal?

Robot 1-X, save my friends! And Zoidberg! I just told you! You've killed me! You don't know how to do any of those. No! I want to live! There are still too many things I don't own! As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead.

Morbo can't understand his teleprompter because he forgot how you say that letter that's shaped like a man wearing a hat. Spare me your space age technobabble, Attila the Hun! Well I'da done better, but it's plum hard pleading a case while awaiting trial for that there incompetence.

Five hours? Aw, man! Couldn't you just get me the death penalty? Okay, it's 500 dollars, you have no choice of carrier, the battery can't hold the charge and the reception isn't veryà Can I use the gun?
